      public CustomTaxEvent(String identifier, String name, List<Price> prices, String permission, String message, boolean usingIgnore, List<String> ignore, boolean online, boolean deposit)
      Constructs a CustomTaxEvent.
      Parameters:
      identifier - The identifier of the event as the key in the configuration.
      name - The name of the event.
      prices - Prices that will be deducted from the player.
      permission - The permission required to call this event.
      message - The message that will be sent to the player.
      usingIgnore - Whether the event is including the default ignore list.
      ignore - The list of Permissions, Players or Groups that are not affected.
      online - Whether the event is only called when the player is online.
      deposit - Whether the event will deposit into the global bank
